### Algo Trading Backend API Tests

### 1. Create Strategy - EMA Crossover
POST http://localhost:8080/api/strategies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "EMA Crossover Strategy",
  "instrument": "NIFTY",
  "conditions": [
    {
      "indicator": "EMA",
      "condition": ">",
      "value": "50",
      "logic": "AND"
    },
    {
      "indicator": "RSI",
      "condition": ">",
      "value": "50"
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Create Strategy - RSI Momentum
POST http://localhost:8080/api/strategies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "RSI Momentum",
  "instrument": "BANKNIFTY",
  "conditions": [
    {
      "indicator": "RSI",
      "condition": "<",
      "value": "30",
      "logic": "OR"
    },
    {
      "indicator": "RSI",
      "condition": ">",
      "value": "70"
    }
  ]
}

### 3. Get All Strategies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/strategies

### 4. Get Strategy by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/strategies/1

### 5. Activate Strategy
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/strategies/1/activate

### 6. Deactivate Strategy
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/strategies/1/deactivate

### 7. Run Backtest
POST http://localhost:8080/api/backtest/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31",
  "initialCapital": 100000
}

### 8. Get All Trades
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades

### 9. Get Trades by Strategy
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades/strategy/1

### 10. Get Total PnL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades/pnl/total

### 11. Get PnL by Strategy
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades/pnl/by-strategy

### 12. Get Win Rate
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades/winrate/1

### 13. Delete Strategy
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/strategies/1
